{"tid":1214661,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"6/12警方主動後退，再使用催淚彈","createTime":"2019-06-13T04:58:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T06:04:20.000Z","uid":37907,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5a467e0c88898dbd54e8725d7438c72adbf5cb69","tid":1214661,"uid":37907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:58:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://vimeo.com/341947898\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvimeo.com%2F341947898&d=lXSk0n6jiDV9AqJ6X6RhLrM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=74d2271a\" target=\"_blank\">https://vimeo.com/341947898</a><br />\n<br />\n今朝聽新聞講警方話示威者攻破防線先迫不得已使用催淚彈<br />\n好在有朋友咁啱影低左警方主動後退嘅一刻<br />\n片中睇到左上方警方主動後退，示威者仲要跨過鐵馬先可向前行，兩者之間好多空位，絕對唔係示威者衝擊<br />\n<br />\n之後呢個位置就放催淚彈，請問警方係咪因為冇原因主動放催淚彈，而主動後退，再[ 迫不得已 ]使用催淚彈?"},{"pid":"91cae0f24270263a7fb45ede8e18113d7d0e5bc9","tid":1214661,"uid":185845,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:00:23.000Z","msg":"連黑旗都見唔到喎屌"},{"pid":"5a0d5f9c8ba57cbbdba2ab945492282547aa4677","tid":1214661,"uid":30966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:01:01.000Z","msg":"如果係咁 佢地下次再退就要準備好水"},{"pid":"1d48774b1a3b0ea78f2a39f5f6f91c4d4c7ccf18","tid":1214661,"uid":37907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:13:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://vimeo.com/341951468\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvimeo.com%2F341951468&d=lXSk0n6jiDV9AqJ6X6RhLrM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=0c51437c\" target=\"_blank\">https://vimeo.com/341951468</a><br />\n<br />\n下集，放催淚彈嘅一刻，係冇旗喎"},{"pid":"e4f0e1e5fa8450c547cde47b32d86398ce74825d","tid":1214661,"uid":185845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:17:18.000Z","msg":"仆街，咁咪即係引你入去再屈你衝擊"},{"pid":"5684d92b4f0572748cbe09077965edb51e9897d1","tid":1214661,"uid":185845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:17:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e5b41eafe7897177b97d3f7000626985351e173b","ti